{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"600013e1-4c51-58d0-80e2-04e1a2fcb39c","frontmatter":{"title":"使用 Nokogiri 解析 HTML","date":"2016/05/28","tags":["Ruby"],"issueId":19},"fields":{"slug":"使用Nokogiri解析HTML"},"excerpt":"Nokogiri 是 Ruby 的一个 HTML/XML 文件的解析库。在需要解析 HTML/XML 文件获取数据时，它是一个很好的选择。 解析 HTML 文档 使用   解析 HTML 将会生成  。\n生成该对象的方式有三种，分别是通过字符串解析，通过文件解析，通过网络解析。…","html":"<p>Nokogiri 是 Ruby 的一个 HTML/XML 文件的解析库。在需要解析 HTML/XML 文件获取数据时，它是一个很好的选择。</p>\n<h2 id=\"解析-HTML-文档\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90-HTML-%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3\" aria-label=\"解析 HTML 文档 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>解析 HTML 文档</h2>\n<p>使用 <code class=\"language-text\">Nokogiri</code> 解析 HTML 将会生成 <code class=\"language-text\">Nokogiri documens</code>。\n生成该对象的方式有三种，分别是通过字符串解析，通过文件解析，通过网络解析。</p>\n<h3 id=\"通过字符串解析\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90\" aria-label=\"通过字符串解析 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>通过字符串解析</h3>\n<p>通过字符串解析，即是将字符串当作函数的参数传给 <code class=\"language-text\">Nokogiri::HTML</code> 函数。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">doc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">Nokogiri</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token constant\">HTML</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;html>&lt;body>&lt;h1>Ahonn&lt;/h1>&lt;/body>&lt;/html>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<!--more-->\n<h3 id=\"通过文件解析\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90\" aria-label=\"通过文件解析 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>通过文件解析</h3>\n<p>通过文件解析需要打开文件，并将文件内容当作参数。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">doc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">File</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>open<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"index.html\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>f<span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token constant\">Nokogiri</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token constant\">HTML</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>f<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"通过网络解析\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90\" aria-label=\"通过网络解析 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>通过网络解析</h3>\n<p>这是最常用的形式，即使用 <code class=\"language-text\">open-uri</code> 打开对应的网址，并返回字符串给 <code class=\"language-text\">Nokogiri</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\"><span class=\"token keyword\">require</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"open-uri\"</span>\ndoc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">Nokogiri</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token constant\">HTMl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>open<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"http://www.ahonn.me\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"搜索-HTML-文档\"><a href=\"#%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2-HTML-%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3\" aria-label=\"搜索 HTML 文档 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>搜索 HTML 文档</h2>\n<p>Nokogiri 提供 xpath 以及 css 选择器这两种方式来搜索 HTML 文档，使得我们能够获取到对应的需要的节点及数据。</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">xpath</code> 方法以及 <code class=\"language-text\">css</code> 方法返回的是一个节点结果集。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">doc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">Nokogiri</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token constant\">HTML</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>open<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"http://www.ahonn.me\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\ndoc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>xpath<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"//title\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\ndoc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>css<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\".nav-list a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># ['&lt;a href=\"/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"nav-list-link active\">Home&lt;/a>',</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># '&lt;a href=\"/archives/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"nav-list-link\">Archives&lt;/a>',</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># '&lt;a href=\"/tags/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"nav-list-link\">Tags&lt;/a>',</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># '&lt;a href=\"/about/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"nav-list-link\">About&lt;/a>']</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"获取单个结果\"><a href=\"#%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C\" aria-label=\"获取单个结果 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>获取单个结果</h3>\n<p>如果想要返回单个结果，可以使用 <code class=\"language-text\">at_xpath</code> 或者 <code class=\"language-text\">at_css</code> 方法来获取结果集中的第一个元素。\n就是说返回的不再是结果集，而是元素节点。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">doc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>at_css<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\".nav-list a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># &lt;a href=\"/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"nav-list-link active\">Home&lt;/a></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"获取元素属性\"><a href=\"#%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7\" aria-label=\"获取元素属性 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>获取元素属性</h3>\n<p>还可通过 <code class=\"language-text\">.</code> 或者索引来获取元素的属性：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">links <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> doc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>css<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\".nav-list a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nputs links<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token comment\"># 4</span>\nputs links<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>text <span class=\"token comment\"># Home</span>\nputs links<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'href'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># /archives/</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"限制选择器\"><a href=\"#%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%99%A8\" aria-label=\"限制选择器 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>限制选择器</h3>\n<p>Nokogiri 还提供了自定义筛选的限制选择器，返回结果集中符合条件的元素：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">links <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> doc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>css<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\".nav-list a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>select<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>link<span class=\"token operator\">|</span> link<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'href'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/archives/\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nlinks<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">each</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>link<span class=\"token operator\">|</span> puts link<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>text <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># Archives</span></code></pre></div>","timeToRead":2}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"600013e1-4c51-58d0-80e2-04e1a2fcb39c"}}